WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:23.314 --> 00:00:26.192 position:50% align:center
[AI] Good thing
it's sunny today, huh?

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:28.403 position:50% align:center
By the way, I'm Ai Ohto.

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:32.198 position:50% align:center
Um, your clothes are cute.

00:00:32.282 --> 00:00:34.576 position:50% align:center
Where'd you get them?

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:40.832 position:50% align:center
For real, though. Great weather.

00:00:50.467 --> 00:00:53.636 position:50% align:center
So, isn't it hard to
protect that many Eggs?

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:55.764 position:50% align:center
How do you do it?

00:00:55.847 --> 00:00:58.892 position:50% align:center
Ever had these,
they're pretty tasty!

00:01:02.062 --> 00:01:04.856 position:50% align:center
Can I ask you a question?

00:01:07.025 --> 00:01:08.777 position:50% align:center
Of course, ask away!

00:01:13.031 --> 00:01:14.115 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Tell me.

00:01:14.199 --> 00:01:16.534 position:50% align:center
Who are you fighting for?

00:01:16.618 --> 00:01:19.329 position:50% align:center
[AI]
That's easy... for Koito.

00:01:19.412 --> 00:01:20.914 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Who's Koito?

00:01:20.997 --> 00:01:23.375 position:50% align:center
She's my best friend.

00:01:23.458 --> 00:01:29.005 position:50% align:center
Ah. Are you sure
it's not for yourself?

00:01:29.089 --> 00:01:31.007 position:50% align:center
How do you mean?

00:01:31.091 --> 00:01:34.260 position:50% align:center
You don't like
who you are, so you go.

00:01:34.344 --> 00:01:36.096 position:50% align:center
Even if you're afraid.

00:01:36.179 --> 00:01:38.723 position:50% align:center
You want to change
the self you hate.

00:01:38.807 --> 00:01:41.101 position:50% align:center
That you, too?

00:01:41.184 --> 00:01:42.727 position:50% align:center
No, I'm not like you.

00:01:42.811 --> 00:01:45.063 position:50% align:center
I actually love myself.

00:01:45.146 --> 00:01:48.233 position:50% align:center
So why do you do it, then?

00:01:48.316 --> 00:01:49.901 position:50% align:center
For my sister.

00:01:49.984 --> 00:01:51.319 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Does that mean...?

00:01:51.403 --> 00:01:53.571 position:50% align:center
I let her die.

00:03:29.626 --> 00:03:31.628 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I'm home.

00:03:35.090 --> 00:03:38.343 position:50% align:center
You're back. That's good.

00:03:39.344 --> 00:03:40.553 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Ohto.

00:03:40.637 --> 00:03:41.846 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Hm?

00:03:41.930 --> 00:03:43.264 position:50% align:center
How are your injuries?

00:03:43.348 --> 00:03:44.933 position:50% align:center
Do you feel better?

00:03:46.601 --> 00:03:48.603 position:50% align:center
Your mother's very worried.

00:03:48.687 --> 00:03:50.146 position:50% align:center
So, please, Ohto.

00:03:50.230 --> 00:03:52.857 position:50% align:center
Will you tell us
what happened to you?

00:03:55.193 --> 00:03:57.404 position:50% align:center
Now, Ai.

00:03:57.487 --> 00:03:58.488 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
It's fine.

00:03:58.571 --> 00:04:01.741 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
I'm sorry.

00:04:01.825 --> 00:04:06.371 position:50% align:center
Ohto. Is it possible
you hate me?

00:04:06.454 --> 00:04:08.206 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I don't...

00:04:08.289 --> 00:04:10.959 position:50% align:center
I mean, not really.

00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:12.252 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
That's a relief.

00:04:13.253 --> 00:04:15.755 position:50% align:center
[TV]
What the what?

00:04:19.592 --> 00:04:21.720 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:04:21.803 --> 00:04:24.055 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Here. This is my contact info.

00:04:24.139 --> 00:04:27.100 position:50% align:center
Message me when you
want to change plans.

00:04:27.183 --> 00:04:28.560 position:50% align:center
I'll buy Eggs on odd days,

00:04:28.643 --> 00:04:31.312 position:50% align:center
and you can buy them
on even ones.

00:04:31.396 --> 00:04:33.940 position:50% align:center
That way we don't
have to meet again.

00:04:40.739 --> 00:04:43.575 position:50% align:center
Good luck. And one more thing,

00:04:43.658 --> 00:04:45.618 position:50% align:center
don't abuse my number.

00:04:48.246 --> 00:04:49.831 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Yeah, right.

00:05:03.345 --> 00:05:06.348 position:50% align:center
Aah!

00:05:08.516 --> 00:05:11.353 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:05:16.608 --> 00:05:19.611 position:50% align:center
So, as long as
I don't crack the Egg,

00:05:19.694 --> 00:05:21.821 position:50% align:center
nothing will bad
will happen to me.

00:05:21.905 --> 00:05:24.783 position:50% align:center
Guess the Seeno Evils see no Ai!

00:05:26.117 --> 00:05:27.702 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:05:30.622 --> 00:05:31.915 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:05:38.088 --> 00:05:39.798 position:50% align:center
[crack]

00:05:49.015 --> 00:05:51.559 position:50% align:center
Okay. Stay there.

00:05:54.145 --> 00:05:57.732 position:50% align:center
♪ march-style music playing ♪

00:05:57.816 --> 00:05:59.734 position:50% align:center
Oookay.

00:05:59.818 --> 00:06:01.611 position:50% align:center
Hello?

00:06:03.571 --> 00:06:06.783 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Sorry, we'll talk later!

00:06:06.866 --> 00:06:08.410 position:50% align:center
Come on!

00:06:09.494 --> 00:06:12.163 position:50% align:center
Uh. Wait, what's happening?

00:06:13.415 --> 00:06:15.583 position:50% align:center
Is this a school?

00:06:15.667 --> 00:06:18.336 position:50% align:center
Hold on, where are you going?

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:23.258 position:50% align:center
That hurt.

00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:26.594 position:50% align:center
You okay?

00:06:26.678 --> 00:06:27.929 position:50% align:center
Whoa, come back!

00:06:28.013 --> 00:06:30.223 position:50% align:center
I'll protect you!

00:06:41.026 --> 00:06:43.028 position:50% align:center
Wow. Thank you.

00:06:48.867 --> 00:06:50.410 position:50% align:center
[AI]
This way!

00:06:50.994 --> 00:06:52.620 position:50% align:center
Hurry! The door!

00:07:02.255 --> 00:07:03.131 position:50% align:center
There we go.

00:07:03.214 --> 00:07:05.258 position:50% align:center
That should buy us some time.

00:07:05.342 --> 00:07:06.426 position:50% align:center
Sorry about this.

00:07:06.509 --> 00:07:08.303 position:50% align:center
I didn't mean--

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:14.976 position:50% align:center
Are you all right?

00:07:15.060 --> 00:07:17.062 position:50% align:center
My name's Ai Ohto.

00:07:17.145 --> 00:07:19.147 position:50% align:center
I'm Minami Suzuhara.

00:07:19.230 --> 00:07:20.440 position:50% align:center
Don't worry, okay?

00:07:20.523 --> 00:07:23.943 position:50% align:center
I promise I'll
protect you to save Koito.

00:07:24.027 --> 00:07:25.528 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
Who's that?

00:07:27.655 --> 00:07:30.742 position:50% align:center
Is Koito your friend?

00:07:30.825 --> 00:07:32.452 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Mm.

00:07:32.535 --> 00:07:34.162 position:50% align:center
I'm kind of jealous.

00:07:34.245 --> 00:07:37.165 position:50% align:center
I really wish I had
a friend like that.

00:07:39.584 --> 00:07:40.418 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:07:40.502 --> 00:07:42.879 position:50% align:center
What's wrong?

00:07:42.962 --> 00:07:45.256 position:50% align:center
So, what's up with the leotard?

00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:46.633 position:50% align:center
Oh. Uh.

00:07:46.716 --> 00:07:48.843 position:50% align:center
I'm in the gymnastics club.

00:07:48.927 --> 00:07:50.136 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I knew it!

00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:52.347 position:50% align:center
I could tell by
your awesome figure.

00:07:54.849 --> 00:07:56.810 position:50% align:center
It's not a super big deal.

00:07:56.893 --> 00:07:59.396 position:50% align:center
My coach was always yelling
at me not to lose it.

00:07:59.479 --> 00:08:01.690 position:50% align:center
I'm a hermit,
so I've got no muscles.

00:08:01.773 --> 00:08:03.650 position:50% align:center
Wanna see my noodle legs?

00:08:03.733 --> 00:08:05.235 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
You're a hermit?

00:08:05.318 --> 00:08:07.737 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I'm pretty hopeless!

00:08:09.447 --> 00:08:11.241 position:50% align:center
That's cool.

00:08:11.324 --> 00:08:12.450 position:50% align:center
Maybe it's weird,

00:08:12.534 --> 00:08:14.911 position:50% align:center
but I'd give anything
to be more like you.

00:08:14.994 --> 00:08:16.871 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Uh, I don't follow.

00:08:16.955 --> 00:08:18.665 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
Okay. So, one time,

00:08:18.748 --> 00:08:20.291 position:50% align:center
I decided that I was
going to blow off

00:08:20.375 --> 00:08:22.252 position:50% align:center
my morning gymnastics practice.

00:08:22.335 --> 00:08:23.378 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Oh yeah?

00:08:23.461 --> 00:08:25.422 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
I really wanted to stay in bed.

00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:27.132 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Mm. Who doesn't?

00:08:27.215 --> 00:08:28.341 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
And I always wanted to see

00:08:28.425 --> 00:08:30.802 position:50% align:center
what morning rush hour
would be like.

00:08:30.885 --> 00:08:31.886 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Uh-huh?

00:08:31.970 --> 00:08:34.055 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
But because I psyched myself up.

00:08:34.139 --> 00:08:36.391 position:50% align:center
I just tossed
and turned all night.

00:08:36.474 --> 00:08:37.475 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Been there!

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:38.977 position:50% align:center
So did you just sleep all day?

00:08:39.060 --> 00:08:40.020 position:50% align:center
How'd it go?

00:08:40.103 --> 00:08:41.271 position:50% align:center
In the end,

00:08:41.354 --> 00:08:44.482 position:50% align:center
I went to morning practice
without sleeping.

00:08:44.566 --> 00:08:46.818 position:50% align:center
I was out of it from staying up.

00:08:46.901 --> 00:08:48.069 position:50% align:center
Naturally,

00:08:48.153 --> 00:08:50.488 position:50% align:center
my coach gave me a
really hard time that day.

00:08:50.572 --> 00:08:52.657 position:50% align:center
[AI] Well, if you ask me,
that sounds way more impressive

00:08:52.741 --> 00:08:55.243 position:50% align:center
than anything I've ever done.

00:08:55.326 --> 00:08:59.247 position:50% align:center
Maybe, but I wish I were
stronger like you, Ohto.

00:09:00.582 --> 00:09:01.833 position:50% align:center
Don't worry.

00:09:01.916 --> 00:09:04.753 position:50% align:center
I'm gonna protect you,
so let's survive together.

00:09:04.836 --> 00:09:06.338 position:50% align:center
'Kay.

00:09:06.421 --> 00:09:08.548 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] It will take more than
that to bring your friend back.

00:09:08.631 --> 00:09:09.799 position:50% align:center
Uh.

00:09:11.676 --> 00:09:12.761 position:50% align:center
Where?

00:09:12.844 --> 00:09:15.305 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
I'm over here! This way.

00:09:17.515 --> 00:09:19.684 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] In order
to free the captured maiden,

00:09:19.768 --> 00:09:22.354 position:50% align:center
you'll have to defeat
the Wonder Killer.

00:09:22.437 --> 00:09:24.522 position:50% align:center
Sorry, a wonder what now?

00:09:24.606 --> 00:09:26.941 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] Oh, I thought it
would be easier to understand

00:09:27.025 --> 00:09:28.193 position:50% align:center
if they had a cool name.

00:09:28.276 --> 00:09:31.071 position:50% align:center
Don't we just have
to survive until the bell?

00:09:31.154 --> 00:09:33.948 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] That's ridiculous;
do you really think running away

00:09:34.032 --> 00:09:35.742 position:50% align:center
would solve anything?

00:09:35.825 --> 00:09:38.370 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Stand up and fight, young lady!

00:09:38.453 --> 00:09:40.413 position:50% align:center
[AI]
What am I supposed to fight?

00:09:40.497 --> 00:09:42.040 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
The Wonder Killer.

00:09:42.123 --> 00:09:44.125 position:50% align:center
It's the form
of an Egg's trauma.

00:09:44.209 --> 00:09:47.128 position:50% align:center
The two are inexplicably
drawn to each other.

00:09:47.212 --> 00:09:48.880 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
To take down a Wonder Killer,

00:09:48.963 --> 00:09:51.007 position:50% align:center
[distorted]
you need to -your- power.

00:09:51.091 --> 00:09:53.843 position:50% align:center
[AI]
What? You're breaking up!

00:09:53.927 --> 00:09:55.804 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
I think something's here.

00:09:55.887 --> 00:09:57.764 position:50% align:center
At the door!

00:09:59.599 --> 00:10:02.310 position:50% align:center
[COACH] Is that dumb
delinquent rubbing off on you?

00:10:02.394 --> 00:10:05.230 position:50% align:center
Guess I can't leave
you alone, can I?

00:10:05.313 --> 00:10:06.981 position:50% align:center
What's this lady's problem?

00:10:07.065 --> 00:10:08.316 position:50% align:center
Get back to work.

00:10:08.400 --> 00:10:10.235 position:50% align:center
You need to practice, Suzuhara.

00:10:10.318 --> 00:10:11.569 position:50% align:center
--Now!
--[gasps]

00:10:11.653 --> 00:10:13.530 position:50% align:center
I'm so sorry, coach!

00:10:13.613 --> 00:10:15.407 position:50% align:center
Wait. Your coach?

00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:17.575 position:50% align:center
She's your trauma?

00:10:17.659 --> 00:10:20.537 position:50% align:center
Are you trying to say
my teaching is traumatic?

00:10:20.620 --> 00:10:22.205 position:50% align:center
Don't be rude.

00:10:22.288 --> 00:10:24.249 position:50% align:center
You stay away from her.

00:10:24.332 --> 00:10:25.417 position:50% align:center
Now I'm really a--

00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:26.501 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
No, don't!

00:10:26.584 --> 00:10:28.795 position:50% align:center
It's because I'm no good.

00:10:28.878 --> 00:10:30.755 position:50% align:center
--Huh?
--[COACH] That's right.

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:33.508 position:50% align:center
You simply don't have
enough spirit, Suzuhara.

00:10:33.591 --> 00:10:34.342 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
I'm sorry.

00:10:34.426 --> 00:10:36.511 position:50% align:center
I'll... I'll try harder.

00:10:36.594 --> 00:10:37.887 position:50% align:center
What do you mean?

00:10:37.971 --> 00:10:40.598 position:50% align:center
Wasn't it so bad you
couldn't take it anymore?

00:10:40.682 --> 00:10:42.434 position:50% align:center
No, it's all my fault.

00:10:42.517 --> 00:10:45.895 position:50% align:center
Coach has to be hard on me
because I'm so hopeless.

00:10:48.982 --> 00:10:51.401 position:50% align:center
No. Minami.

00:10:51.484 --> 00:10:53.653 position:50% align:center
Get away from her!

00:11:02.954 --> 00:11:05.415 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Minami. I have to...

00:11:07.876 --> 00:11:09.878 position:50% align:center
What is all this?

00:11:09.961 --> 00:11:12.213 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Just your classic harassment.

00:11:12.297 --> 00:11:14.549 position:50% align:center
But why would anyone
do this to you?

00:11:14.632 --> 00:11:16.634 position:50% align:center
Is it because you're
friends with me?

00:11:16.718 --> 00:11:18.636 position:50% align:center
I doubt it.

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:20.096 position:50% align:center
I've heard them
say Mister Sawaki

00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:22.223 position:50% align:center
is giving me special treatment.

00:11:22.307 --> 00:11:23.683 position:50% align:center
They're probably just jealous.

00:11:23.767 --> 00:11:26.603 position:50% align:center
Well, of course he is,
you're a transfer student.

00:11:26.686 --> 00:11:29.564 position:50% align:center
Heh. A girl's jealousy
sure is scary.

00:11:29.647 --> 00:11:31.608 position:50% align:center
You know?

00:11:31.691 --> 00:11:33.818 position:50% align:center
[AI]
This isn't funny.

00:11:34.027 --> 00:11:36.863 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT A laughing]
Oh my god, this is too much.

00:11:36.946 --> 00:11:39.491 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT B laughing]
Come on, face this way.

00:11:39.574 --> 00:11:41.368 position:50% align:center
--[KOITO] Stop it.
--[STUDENT A] Make us.

00:11:46.206 --> 00:11:47.916 position:50% align:center
Are you okay?

00:11:54.089 --> 00:11:56.758 position:50% align:center
You got it? Right, Ai?

00:12:04.182 --> 00:12:07.811 position:50% align:center
Sorry. I was scared.

00:12:08.353 --> 00:12:10.355 position:50% align:center
Scared of being left out.

00:12:12.774 --> 00:12:15.860 position:50% align:center
So, you were scared. It's okay.

00:12:15.944 --> 00:12:16.945 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I'm really sorry.

00:12:17.028 --> 00:12:18.196 position:50% align:center
It's not your fault.

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:19.823 position:50% align:center
I know you tried your best.

00:12:19.906 --> 00:12:21.116 position:50% align:center
It's okay.

00:12:21.199 --> 00:12:25.328 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:12:25.412 --> 00:12:27.580 position:50% align:center
I'm so sorry.

00:12:35.380 --> 00:12:37.507 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
I feel sorry for Minami.

00:12:37.590 --> 00:12:41.011 position:50% align:center
I mean, what's so strong
about you, anyway?

00:12:41.094 --> 00:12:44.431 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Shut up. I'm trying.

00:12:45.807 --> 00:12:47.684 position:50% align:center
I will change.

00:12:52.897 --> 00:12:54.441 position:50% align:center
[COACH]
Is that what your problem is?

00:12:54.524 --> 00:12:56.735 position:50% align:center
This extra weight
is from your period?

00:12:56.818 --> 00:12:59.821 position:50% align:center
Take gymnastics
more seriously, damn it!

00:12:59.904 --> 00:13:01.281 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
I'm sorry, Coach.

00:13:01.364 --> 00:13:02.615 position:50% align:center
Please forgive me.

00:13:02.699 --> 00:13:03.825 position:50% align:center
[COACH]
Just so you know,

00:13:03.908 --> 00:13:05.869 position:50% align:center
this isn't considered
corporal punishment.

00:13:05.952 --> 00:13:07.078 position:50% align:center
It's tough love.

00:13:07.162 --> 00:13:10.081 position:50% align:center
I do it because I love
and care about you.

00:13:10.165 --> 00:13:13.251 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
Yes. Right.

00:13:15.086 --> 00:13:16.379 position:50% align:center
Once you're a good girl,

00:13:16.463 --> 00:13:18.882 position:50% align:center
I'll be sure to finish you off
nice and painlessly.

00:13:18.965 --> 00:13:21.134 position:50% align:center
How does that sound?

00:13:21.217 --> 00:13:23.845 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
Very good. Thank you.

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:27.390 position:50% align:center
Is that Ohto?

00:13:28.892 --> 00:13:32.395 position:50% align:center
All right bitch,
time for you to die!

00:13:43.156 --> 00:13:44.532 position:50% align:center
[MINAMI]
Stop it!

00:13:44.616 --> 00:13:46.409 position:50% align:center
I brought this on myself!

00:13:46.493 --> 00:13:48.411 position:50% align:center
Please just leave me alone!

00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:49.579 position:50% align:center
It's because

00:13:49.662 --> 00:13:51.581 position:50% align:center
